Sourceforge has made some changes in their CVS servers, and now the 
server name contains the project name.  This means that 
"cvs.sourceforge.net" should be replaced by 
"cantera.cvs.sourceforge.net" when checking out cantera.

If you are accessing Cantera using CVS, you should check out a new 
working copy, so that "cvs update" will work correctly.
